law.catch_line: The hours specified in §§ 11-301 to 11-303, inclusive, of this article apply except as modified by...
law.text: The hours specified in §§ 11-301 to 11-303, inclusive, of this article apply except as modified by §§ 11-203, 11-304, 11-305, and 11-401 through 11-524, inclusive, of this article.
